'''白血病抑制因子'''（Leukemia inhibitory factor，缩写 '''LIF'''）是一種屬於[[白细胞介素-6|白介素-6]]大類的[[細胞因子|細胞因子]]。它能通過抑制分化影響[[細胞|細胞]]生长。LIF水平下降會使細胞開始分化。

==功能==
白血病抑制因子能夠誘導[[骨髓性白血病|骨髓性白血病]]細胞的末端分化，進而阻止其生長，因而得名。白血病抑制因子還有以下功能：能促進多種細胞的生長與分化，影響[[骨|骨]][[代謝|代謝]]、[[惡病質體|惡病質體]]、{{link-en|神經發育|Neural development}}，[[胚胎發育|胚胎發育]]以及[[炎症|炎症]]作用。受p53調控的白血病抑制因子能促進小鼠和人的胚胎[[着床|着床]]<ref>{{cite journal
 |url          = http://www.nature.com/nature/journal/v450/n7170/abs/nature05993.html
 |journal      = Nature
 |date         = November 29, 2007
 |title        = p53 regulates maternal reproduction through LIF
 |author       = Wenwei Hu, Zhaohui Feng, Angelika K. Teresky1, Arnold J. Levine
 |volume       = 450
 |issue        = 7170
 |pages        = 721–724
 |doi          = 10.1038/nature05993
 |pmid         = 18046411
 |access-date  = 2017-01-27
 |archive-date = 2017-03-15
 |archive-url  = https://web.archive.org/web/20170315200729/http://www.nature.com/nature/journal/v450/n7170/abs/nature05993.html
 |dead-url     = no
}}</ref>。一篇文章提出重組人白血病抑制因子可能可以提高意外懷孕的婦女（體內胚胎）的着床成功率<ref>{{cite journal|last=Aghajanova|title=Leukemia inhibitory factor and human embryo implantation|pmid=15731310|year=2004|first1=L|volume=1034|pages=176–83|doi=10.1196/annals.1335.020|journal=Annals of the New York Academy of Sciences}}</ref>。

==表達==
LIF在正常情況下會由[[囊胚_(哺乳動物)|囊胚]]中的[[滋養層|滋養層]]（TE）表達，而其受體LIFR則會由[[內細胞群|內細胞群]]（ICM）的細胞表達。[[胚胎幹細胞|胚胎幹細胞]]取自內細胞群的細胞，在體外培養時就需要額外補充LIF。目前，重組LIF已可以通過基因工程的手段由植物（[[水稻|水稻]]）產生<ref>{{cite journal|author=Bradford A. Youngblood et al.|title=Application of recombinant human leukemia inhibitory factor (LIF) produced in rice (''Oryza sativa L.'') for maintenance of mouse embryonic stem cells|journal=Journal of Biotechnology Volume 172|date=2014-02-20|pages=67–72}}</ref>。

==幹細胞培養==
幹細胞培養基中大都含有LIF，可用於替代餵養層（feeder layer）細胞，因爲餵養層細胞的主要作用即產生LIF。不表達LIF基因的餵養層細胞難以支持幹細胞的培養<ref>{{cite journal |pmid= 1522892|year= 1992|author1= Stewart|first1= C. L.|title= Blastocyst implantation depends on maternal expression of leukaemia inhibitory factor|journal= Nature|volume= 359|issue= 6390|pages= 76–9|last2= Kaspar|first2= P|last3= Brunet|first3= L. J.|last4= Bhatt|first4= H|last5= Gadi|first5= I|last6= Köntgen|first6= F|last7= Abbondanzo|first7= S. J.|doi= 10.1038/359076a0}}</ref>。LIF通過招募信號誘導分子以及轉錄激活因子3（[[STAT3|STAT3]]）促進細胞的自我更新。活化的LIFR能徵募Stat3。隨後，[[JAK激酶|JAK激酶]]能將其磷酸化。不過LIF和Stat3是不足以阻止細胞分化的，一旦移去培養基中的血清，幹細胞就會分化。在原生[[細胞潛能|多能性]]幹細胞分化的可逆階段，加入LIF可以使細胞重回原生多能性階段<ref>{{cite journal | last=Martello | first=Graziano | last2=Smith | first2=Austin |year=2014 |title=The Nature of Embryonic Stem Cells |journal=Annual Review Cell Developmental Biology | volume=30 | pages=647 |doi=10.1146/annurev-cellbio-100913-013116}}</ref><ref>{{cite journal |author=Kawahara Y, Manabe T, Matsumoto M, Kajiume T, Matsumoto M, Yuge L |title=LIF-Free Embryonic Stem Cell Culture in Simulated Microgravity |journal=PLoS ONE |volume=4 |issue=7 |pages=e6343 |year=2009 |pmid=19626124 |pmc=2710515 |doi=10.1371/journal.pone.0006343 |url=http://www.plosone.org/article/info%3Adoi%2F10.1371%2Fjournal.pone.0006343 |editor1-last=Zwaka |editor1-first=Thomas |access-date=2017-01-27 |archive-date=2014-02-22 |archive-url=https://web.archive.org/web/20140222044719/http://www.plosone.org/article/info:doi%2F10.1371%2Fjournal.pone.0006343 |dead-url=no }}</ref><ref>{{cite web |url=http://www.geneticsandsociety.org/article.php?id=5197 |title=CGS : PTO Finds Stem Cell Patent Anticipated, Obvious in Light of 'Significant Guideposts' |work= |accessdate= |archive-url=https://web.archive.org/web/20111004055228/http://www.geneticsandsociety.org/article.php?id=5197 |archive-date=2011-10-04 |dead-url=yes }}</ref>。

